    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Then in <code>docs/.vitepress/config.ts</code>:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The following properties can be overridden for each locale (including root):"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Refer <code>DefaultTheme.Config</code> interface for details on customizing the placeholder texts of the default theme. Don't override <code>themeConfig.algolia</code> or <code>themeConfig.carbonAds</code> at locale-level. Refer Algolia docs for using multilingual search."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "<strong>Pro tip:</strong> Config file can be stored at <code>docs/.vitepress/config/index.ts</code> too. It might help you organize stuff by creating a configuration file per locale and then merge and export them from <code>index.ts</code>."
    },
